{"tid":1804324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"28歲公務員阿進: 腥風血雨，社會太多流血事件，不只是警察，我覺得是『政棍』問題，他們挑起很多衝突。","createTime":"2019-12-31T02:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T04:58:39.000Z","uid":51271,"like":10,"dislike":186,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"e5405d7f5dc5d3158ac1861ad79bf4c44254a645","tid":1804324,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"28歲公務員阿進<br />\n<br />\n「腥風血雨，社會太多流血事件，不只是警察，我覺得是『政棍』問題，他們挑起很多衝突。若果純粹說政府有什麼政策做得不好，我覺得可以用理性和平方法講出來，不要說政府不聽，其實是有聽的。說到修例風波，中間已有很多不同修改，並不是有些人說完全無修改，卻仍然用這樣激進的方法表達，我覺得『唔係咁嘅』（不是太正確）。<br />\n<br />\n我相信警察是有人做得不好，我同意的，但我不覺得這是一個藉口，令其他一般市民可以繼續去做錯，因為別人做得不正確，我們不應該以暴易暴，至少要堅守自己當日的信念：要維持社會的法治而出來，而不是為破壞法治而出來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191231/s00001/1577607269386/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%9e%e6%9c%9b2019%e3%80%91%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9-%e4%bb%a5%e6%9a%b4%e6%98%93%e6%9a%b4-%e6%8a%97%e7%a6%81%e8%92%99%e9%9d%a2%e6%b3%95-721-831%e5%8b%be%e8%b5%b7%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e6%81%90%e6%87%bc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191231%2Fs00001%2F1577607269386%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%259b%259e%25e6%259c%259b2019%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9-%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e6%259a%25b4%25e6%2598%2593%25e6%259a%25b4-%25e6%258a%2597%25e7%25a6%2581%25e8%2592%2599%25e9%259d%25a2%25e6%25b3%2595-721-831%25e5%258b%25be%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e6%2581%2590%25e6%2587%25bc&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=b400131f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191231%2Fs00001%2F1577607269386%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%259b%259e%25e6%259c%259b2019%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9-%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e6%259a%25b4%25e6%2598%2593%25e6%259a%25b4-%25e6%258a%2597%25e7%25a6%2581%25e8%2592%2599%25e9%259d%25a2%25e6%25b3%2595-721-831%25e5%258b%25be%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e6%2581%2590%25e6%2587%25bc&h=cc484d45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191231/s00001/1577607269386/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%9e%e6%9c%9b2019%e3%80%91%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9-%e4%bb%a5%e6%9a%b4%e6%98%93%e6%9a%b4-%e6%8a%97%e7%a6%81%e8%92%99%e9%9d%a2%e6%b3%95-721-831%e5%8b%be%e8%b5%b7%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e6%81%90%e6%87%bc</a>"},{"pid":"36f854a0e507fbfe71f3f74ec1849b90a67c79c5","tid":1804324,"uid":21545,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:12:52.000Z","msg":"要維持社會的法治而出來，而不是為破壞法治而出來。<br />\n<br />\n日月神報又想混淆視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77dba40ede56a315e50a641f2e2abbfcb4a4ecc3","tid":1804324,"uid":137440,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問題係我哋唔係要你修改<br />\n我哋係唔想要<br />\n<br />\n正如我哋唔想食屎<br />\n無論你舊屎改到幾香幾臭<br />\n我哋唔想食就係唔想食"},{"pid":"2164cfe5d312e5ab17c2e3266bcee38c2e7e74fc","tid":1804324,"uid":48631,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:19:02.000Z","msg":"好滾動，睇到咸左=.=<br />\nBtw牙進邊撚到進"},{"pid":"0d373d346ff1690dc2002dc9d9f78c1a541aff1d","tid":1804324,"uid":7365,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:19:39.000Z","msg":"政棍:何君堯<br />\n流血事件:721<br />\n何君堯挑起721"},{"pid":"91b72357a1edbb835e8e3cc8edae715f8191e0a3","tid":1804324,"uid":274722,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:20:55.000Z","msg":"成段文咁多on9藍屍主觀觀點：<br />\n『政棍』問題，他們挑起很多衝突。不要說政府不聽，其實是有聽的。<br />\n一般市民可以繼續去做錯<br />\n為破壞法治而出來"},{"pid":"613e3ebcdbd077a6fca07ea79a702d2b72db9d22","tid":1804324,"uid":81052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"聽左有錢佬講去修改呀嘛"},{"pid":"6f2424815f205ae377b795a5c76aed352de7a55f","tid":1804324