碼7成黃2成不理世事"},{"pid":"d8cc2833bbe787272144446b4f401bb526c6e5b1","tid":1804324,"uid":140246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:07:21.000Z","msg":"以為個名叫何進。"},{"pid":"684cc2221e56ce06aba6af1cc0a5f509700debeb","tid":1804324,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:08:01.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=4755c346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"87ba130aea147ea35df9bd9b364f6b80905085df","tid":1804324,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"咁易煽動，點解共產黨煽動唔到香港人親中"},{"pid":"7e9d5716aa0dec6ae7902db8447b207320da8729","tid":1804324,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5405d7f5dc5d3158ac1861ad79bf4c44254a645","tid":1804324,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"28歲公務員阿進<br />\n<br />\n「腥風血雨，社會太多流血事件，不只是警察，我覺得是『政棍』問題，他們挑起很多衝突。若果純粹說政府有什麼政策做得不好，我覺得可以用理性和平方法講出來，不要說政府不聽，其實是有聽的。說到修例風波，中間已有很多不同修改，並不是有些人說完全無修改，卻仍然用這樣激進的方法表達，我覺得『唔係咁嘅』（不是太正確）。<br />\n<br />\n我相信警察是有人做得不好，我同意的，但我不覺得這是一個藉口，令其他一般市民可以繼續去做錯，因為別人做得不正確，我們不應該以暴易暴，至少要堅守自己當日的信念：要維持社會的法治而出來，而不是為破壞法治而出來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191231/s00001/1577607269386/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%9e%e6%9c%9b2019%e3%80%91%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9-%e4%bb%a5%e6%9a%b4%e6%98%93%e6%9a%b4-%e6%8a%97%e7%a6%81%e8%92%99%e9%9d%a2%e6%b3%95-721-831%e5%8b%be%e8%b5%b7%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e6%81%90%e6%87%bc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191231%2Fs00001%2F1577607269386%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%259b%259e%25e6%259c%259b2019%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9-%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e6%259a%25b4%25e6%2598%2593%25e6%259a%25b4-%25e6%258a%2597%25e7%25a6%2581%25e8%2592%2599%25e9%259d%25a2%25e6%25b3%2595-721-831%25e5%258b%25be%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e6%2581%2590%25e6%2587%25bc&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=b400131f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191231%2Fs00001%2F1577607269386%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%259b%259e%25e6%259c%259b2019%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9-%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e6%259a%25b4%25e6%2598%2593%25e6%259a%25b4-%25e6%258a%2597%25e7%25a6%2581%25e8%2592%2599%25e9%259d%25a2%25e6%25b3%2595-721-831%25e5%258b%25be%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e6%2581%2590%25e6%2587%25bc&h=cc484d45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191231/s00001/1577607269386/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%9e%e6%9c%9b2019%e3%80%91%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9-%e4%bb%a5%e6%9a%b4%e6%98%93%e6%9a%b4-%e6%8a%97%e7%a6%81%e8%92%99%e9%9d%a2%e6%b3%95-721-831%e5%8b%be%e8%b5%b7%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e6%81%90%e6%87%bc</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:09:11.000Z","msg":"政棍=特首，葉劉等等<br />\n<br />\n1. 世界上有一個方法叫公投同普選，和平理性非暴力咁比人民表達意見。政府唔做搞到人要用其他方法。<br />\n<br />\n2. 回應 &quot;我覺得可以用理性和平方法講出來，不要說政府不聽，其實是有聽的。說到修例風波，中間已有很多不同修改，並不是有些人說完全無修改，卻仍然用這樣激進的方法表達，我覺得『唔係咁嘅』（不是太正確）。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我警察覺得可以用理性和平方法講佢地想市民離開既意願出來，不要說市民不聽，其實是有聽的。說到離開，其實市民已經退後了，並不是有些人說完全無離開，卻仍然用這樣激進的方法表達(e.g. tg, 水炮車)，我覺得『唔係咁嘅』（不是太正確）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦你"},{"pid":"ec91cc223d8e082f8223bd3dc1c2f665979009ae","tid":1804324,"uid":150315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"超過二百萬人話唔要條例<br />\n政府就話修改<br />\n<br />\n聽說能力咁差都做到公務員?"},{"pid":"7be1c1ac905f9dd66296871136e2f02b38b14fb3","tid":1804324,"uid":66457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"我相信市民是有人做得不好，我同意的，但我不覺得這是一個藉口，令其他警甴可以繼續去做錯，因為我們做得不正確，他們不應該以暴易暴，至少要堅守自己當日的信念：要維持社會的法治而出來，而不是為破壞法治而出來。」"},{"pid":"63637b9d5127088c69646d077db7733f66e33fcc","tid":1804324,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b005ccb274dc1356e1573d67fbca2d164513b197","tid":1804324,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:04:27.000Z","msg":"公務員根本大部份都仆街黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:12:05.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n返緊政府"},{"pid":"a7fb3a0da3c30d9bbac08374ad47e5ddbb9d16e2","tid":1804324,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fac2907709e1a3214c407d8a8d74d2bae5c1ab17","tid":1804324,"uid":42031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f7c11cd57494b97e20dc28c036c414fa266952e1","tid":1804324,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"收皮啦左報<br />\n28歲公務員會講呢啲嘢?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">呢隻毅進仔唔係賤賊我切柒</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:07:08.000Z","msg":"Agree 30以下公務人員起碼7成黃2成不理世事"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"佢咪呢兩成不理世事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2965f6e2a79d504aafbcef8424cff336fe14996","tid":1804324,"uid":111006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"呢d仲仆街過藍屍"},{"pid":"ea563ed5740ebbcc77d66d928671d90fcc27eabf","tid":1804324,"uid":278038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:14:48.000Z","msg":"黑警叫自己做公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},